- Build robust ingestion + timestamp alignment + missingness mask pipeline.
- Implement beat detectors and compute PTT/PAT consistently.
- Prototype dual-encoder Transformer with (1) masked reconstruction and (2) cross-modal contrastive losses on small compute.
